structure.unit: STOCK AND MUTUAL LIFE INSURANCE COMPANIES (Superseded)

law.history: Repealed 1950 Ky. Acts ch. 21, sec. 2. -- Amended 1944 Ky. Acts ch. 161, sec. 2. -- Recodified 1942 Ky. Acts ch. 208, sec. 1, effective October 1, 1942, from Ky. Stat. sec. 659.

metadata.catchline-at-repeal: Ordinary plan life insurance; cash surrender, paid-up insurance or loan value on default of payment of premiums.
